description: TV's smash sci-fi hit comes to BOOM! In what Eureka creator Andrew Cosby calls 'Season 1.5, ' Cosby and writer Brendan Hay (The Daily Show) bring all-new stories from everybody's favorite town of eccentric geniuses! Things start off with a bang when something menacing escapes from Global Dynamics, and it has a target! It's up to Carter and Jo to put together the pieces, but will elements from Jo's past stop her from getting the job done?

The dramatic earth-shattering tie-in follow-up to the previous earth-shattering mini-series that we're gonna release before we start another earth-shattering mini-series that ties into an earth-shattering mini-series after that!!! In this issue, Franklin loves doing whatever he wants! It's up to H.E.R.B.I.E. to keep Franklin out of the Reign (that happens to be Dark, whatever that means)! In this not-really official tie-in to Dark Reign, check out FIVE new stories from the Eisner and Harvey nominee coming this February! Don't take a reign check on this one!

Featuring in this issue:

  • 40-Year-Old-Franklin!
  • Frankenrichards' Monster\1
  • Homework Hassle!
  • The Enemy Of My Enemy Is My Friend!
  • Multiple Personalities!
  • Dark Reigning Cats And Dogs!
name: 40-Year-Old-Franklin; Frankenrichards' Monster; Homework Hassle; The Enemy Of My Enemy Is My Friend; Multiple Personalities; Dark Reigning Cats And Dogs

volume.name: Franklin Richards: Dark Reigning Cats And Dogs

description: When the Balkan conflict tears Sarajevo apart, Srdjan Zivojin, a professor of occult studies, creates a golem of immeasurable power to protect the city's inhabitants from persecution. But the novice magician soon discovers that creating a golem is one thing, but controlling one is another thing altogether! The creature not only has a mind of its own, it intends to 'crush' evil, no matter the consequences... or the collateral damage that results. Armed with a hair trigger temper, and ready to blaze a path of retribution and destruction, Golem introduces an all-new kind of anti-hero, where magic and might combine into an unstoppable force. Evildoers be warned!
name: One Shot

description: Beyond any human justice, Besilov is hunted by his own kind and swears vengeance on the blood traitors who would put him back in chains. Investigating the most lethal case of his career and dangerously distracted by his cousin's disappearance, Baker searches for answers, not knowing it's already too late!

The final chapter of 'Love Stories for Dead People' finds Fig in the basement at the heart of the labyrinth, while Harry and Ann square off against the nightmare that once kept Cain himself awake at night. Meanwhile, the massive party upstairs winds down with unexpected repurcussions. Also featuring a short story illustrated by Eisner Award-winning artist Kyle Baker (PLASTIC MAN).
name: La Belle Et Le Bete Noir: Chapter Five Of Love Stories For Dead People

description: Barock, a fierce god of war from the planet Neboron, must combat a sinister god at an upscale New Jersey mall. During the battle, he saves Zoe - a high maintenance South Jersey girl - and they fall in love. But she won't be moving to the God planet. Instead, Barock will have to buy a house in Cherry Hill, just three houses down from Zoe's mom and dad. How on earth will Barock find the time to carve a single moment to save the galaxy?

In a fabled castle in a mysterious land resides a young prince upon whom the land's very destiny resides. A prince whose bloody and vicious exploits will create a legend that will terrify humanity for generations to come. Except the young prince that Sir Apropos finds is, in fact, a wheezing, pasty-faced nothing nicknamed Flad the Inhaler. And it is up to Apropos to help Flad find his inner impaler, lest an entire country fall to its enemies.
name: Gypsies, Vamps and Thieves, Part Four

description: MAN OF ACTION STUDIOS brings acclaimed Vertigo creator and multiple Eisner nominee STEVEN T. SEAGLE (American Virgin, it's a bird, Sandman Mystery Theater) to Image Comics for the all-new, five-issue series, SOUL KISS - the story of a woman with vengeance on her mind and damnation on her lips. Animator Marco Cinello (The Spongebob Squarepants Movie, Curious George) makes his comics debut providing lush, full-color artwork. A deal with the Devil gone bad leads production assistant Lili Bloom to strike a second deal with the Devil gone worse: To save her boyfriend, Lili must deliver ten innocent souls to Hell by sealing their fateswith a kiss.
name: Chapter 1: Long Road to Ruin

description: Actor Stephen Baldwin and writer Andrew Cosby (creator of Sci-Fi Channel's Eureka) unleash The Remnant at BOOM! Studios! Death tolls are in the thousands all over the planet. Former C.I.A. agent David Sacker tries to put together all the pieces of the puzzle, while trying to release his wife from the clutches of Homeland Security. Sacker might not stay alive long enough to do that with the mysterious John Drouin on his trail.

The Warriors Official Movie Adaptation is something that fans and non-fans alike are sure to dig! In this issue The Warriors are framed for killing Cyrus, a rival gang leader who had been trying to unite all the gangs in the area. With other gangs gunning for them, they must get back to their home turf of Coney Island alive!

name: The Radical Return of Faulty Towers
The Clock That Turned Back Time!
Tales Of The Sphinx Book II
The Big Bang History Of Comics 1
The Big Bang History Of Comics 2
Knight of the Living Dead Part 1
Knight Of The Living Dead Part 2
The Pink Flamingo's Real-Gone Rebop Roost?

description: It's the battle of the century when the Round Table of America and the Tomorrow Syndicate cross paths for the first and only time in comics history to vie for supremacy of the Silver Age. Guest-starring Infra-Man, Horus, N-Man, Hyper-Naut, Infra-Girl & USA. Plus, the three-part confrontation between Mighty Man and the Wicked Worm, complete for the first time in the pages of Big Bang Comics.
name: Big Bang Vs. 1963

description:
Story #1 - Untitled - Donald Duck, Huey, Dewey and Louie

Story #2 - The Dazzle Duck Caper - Uncle Scrooge and The Beagle Boys

Story #3 - The Perfect Spot - Big Bad Wolf and Li'l Bad Wolf

Story #4 - The Indoor Picnic - The Three Pigs, Big Bad Wolf and Li'l Bad Wolf

Story #5 - The Time Trip Gyp - Mickey Mouse and Goofy

1944: World War 2 is raging and the fate of the world hangs in the balance. Adolph Hitler has embraced the supernatural searching for weapons to ensure the victory of his Third Reich - - and he's found it! His secret servant has stolen Thunder Girl's mighty powers and created three super stormtroopers who are wreaking havoc on the Allied troops! THIS ISSUE: The Knights of Justice go to war to battle Hitler's living Blitzkrieg. It is a battle of champions as the blitz races against death in the guise of the Hitler Youth! Venus battles for the souls of innocent soldiers with her old foe "Mary Death", who has been reborn as the Valkyrie. Ultiman faces off against the super soldier Kaptain Thunder while the other Knights contend with that snake in the grass, the Secret Servent!
name: The Super Stormtroopers!

description: The radioactive meteor that collided with a Gemini space capsule in 1964 killed one of the astronauts but transformed the other into the Ultimate Human Being! For forty years, Chris Kelly has fought evil and injustice as Ultiman, inspiring other heroes of the Big Bang universe. THIS ISSUE: Ultiman's girl Friday, Lori Lake, must work overtime when a chimpanzee in the space program develops super powers and makes a monkey out of Ultiman in "The Ultimate Ape!" Also in this issue: When Ultragirl travels to the future to honor a fallen comrade, she and the Pantheon of Heroes face their deadliest foe ever in "Legion of the Dead!" Plus, Thunder Girl models new costumes designed by readers!

volume.name: Big Bang Presents the Ultiman Family
Your Big Book Of Big Bang Comics

description: Warrior Nun Areala is kidnapped by the undead sea captain Edward St. Anthony, who has been cursed by a sea witch to wander the seas forever. He forces her to help him kill the witch to break his curse. But what will Areala do when she discovers the true origin of his curse?
name: Sea Demons; Wrestling With Monsters!

description: Warrior Nun Areala has a sword that can affect humans' souls. But what when she faces a man who claims to be born without a soul? Areala meets the Holy Man!
name: Nemesis; Soul Possession
Winter Jade, Part One; Accursed Event

description: Ninja Nun battles an Oni, a Japanese demon. But the blood she drew from him, was analyzed as being human? Can they catch the Oni/man by setting a trap? And why keep certain policeman disappearing?
name: Winter Jade, Part Two; Kid Stuff
Winter Jade, Part Three; Third Eye

description: Tracing a clue about her true parents, Warrior Nun Areala encounters a little girl that's possessed by a demon. Will Areala learn something about her past?
Ninja Nun fights a fox spirit in Japan! Doughboy tries an assassination attempt on Areala! Shotgun Mary has a dream!

The invaders of Atlantis struggle to deal with increased rebel activity, with the population slowly shifting against there invaders. As Aquaman and the invaders prepare to launch their assault the following day, the prison is attacked with the guards being defeated by Queen Mera in her search for Aquaman. In response to Mera blowing their cover, Aquaman orders the assault to be moved up.  
 
Aquaman then rushes to Meras aid, defeating the last of the remaining guards. However, after the battle he is attacked by Mera's hard water, as she blames him for the death of their child. Aquaman then enacts a plan to wear Mera down to reason with her. All the while the resistant battles the invaders forces, in their effort to reach the palace. Eventually the rebels succeed, killing the Jellyfish while defeating the enemy soldiers who surrender.  
 
As cheers of victory erupt over Atlantis, Aquaman dodges Mera who is impaled on debris, much to Aquaman's regret.
name: Queen to King's Seven

description: The Castle of the Devil hides several secrets-the most horrible of which may still be locked at the base of the castle in the ruins of an ancient abbey. Solomon Kane gets closer to unveiling the truth behind the crazed monks who used to live there, as he deals with the castle's current batch of strange inhabitants. Escaping with John Silent, his wounded companion, is out of the question, because Kane also seeks justice for the souls of innocent children who were killed on the gallows that litter this evil, tainted region of Germany's Black Forest.
name: The Castle of the Devil, Part 5

description:
Zayne Carrick and his crewmates Jarael, Slyssk, and the Mandalorian Rohlan investigate a pleasure cruise gone wrong!

Something horrible has happened aboard the Chancellor Fillorean; the former luxury ship now drifts aimlessly in a space nebula. Upon boarding the ghost ship, a host of asphyxiated passengers and two lone survivors -- a tiny alien and his fierce droid bodyguard -- are all that are found. Zayne and his friends must solve the mystery and find what has been causing the tragic and disturbing deaths -- before they also become victims.
name: Faithful Execution

volume.name: Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic

description: What's life like behind bars for a guy framed for the death of the D.A.'s wife? Ask Cal McDonald. He's a guy who knows a thing or two about misery from first-hand experience, but miserable doesn't begin to describe what's ahead for the disgraced private dick whose only friend on the planet is a dead guy. Now Cal's in lockup at the darkest time of his life with no connection to the outside world except through the random contact he makes with other prisoner. Luckily for Cal, it turns out his reputation proceeds him . . . and the reputation of an ex-cop-gone-wrong who runs with ghouls might be just the thing to keep him alive against all odds.

Heath Huston, a mysterious otherworldly stranger, comes to the rescue of a frontier town that is somehow a step out of time. The peaceful, small mining community is under threat of annihilation when a ruthless land baron arrives with his posse of hired guns to take control of the territory. After the struggle for a peaceable resolution, and the gunfighting . . . it all ends in a down-in-the-mud, cheap-and-bloody fistfight to the death.
name: I Against I (Part 5)

description:
DOWN SOUTH PART 2

The underbelly of Mexico City. A local land baron has hired Moon Knight to ensure the safe return of his kidnapped daughter. But whoever's got the girl is also in the crosshairs of the Punisher, who's traveled down to Mexico on the trail of Russian mobsters. And if that weren't enough, another predator appears to have joined the party. Someone homegrown. Enter Toltec.
name: Down South: Chapter Two

description:
Julien is dying, his body horribly savaged by Lorraine's torturers. His only hope now is Genevieve, but the Castle of the Holy Grail is crawling with the Duke of Lorraine's dreaded Imperial Guard -- not to mention the duke himself.

Fortunately for Genevieve and Julien, Lorraine has other things on his mind -- namely his daughter, Isabelle! Isabelle is drunk with power -- literally -- and she's hell bent on killing her father. Only one of them is going to survive the epic confrontation.

Meanwhile, sniveling Baron Robert Teniers has made his move. He's ready for the deepest mysteries of the Holy Grail, but he should be careful what he wishes for . . .

A sorcerous duel, a grisly ritual, and plenty of bodies pile up in Rex Mundi #16, "First Communion." Heads will roll!

Special guest cover by Buffy cover artist Jo Chen!
name: First Communion

description: FINAL ISSUE! They WERE the New Exiles...but after last issue's shocking ending and a loss that will tear them apart, how can our heroes possibly continue? The answers await you here, true believers, along with clues as to what the future holds for our favorite dimension jumpers! Join X-Maestro Chris Claremont for a bittersweet chapter we can only call "BEGIN ANEW"!
name: Begin Again
